Accuracyedit
As of January 2015 the indicator has been correct 39 out of 48 times as measured by the SampP 500 Index  a success rate of 8112 However since a particular football league winning a Super Bowl and the US Stock market have no real connection this is just a coincidence Therefore there is no reason to expect it will work as a predictor of future bull markets3
